@page "/help"

<PageTitle>User Guide</PageTitle>

<div class="page-header">
    <div>
        <span class="eyebrow">Documentation</span>
        <h1>User Guide</h1>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="form-card">
    <h2>Getting Started</h2>
    <p>
        Samoa Pickleball Hub is designed to help players and organizers manage
        community information in one easy-to-use web application.
    </p>

    <h3>Register and Login</h3>
    <p>
        Users can create an account using the Register link and then log in to access
        authenticated account features.
    </p>

    <h3>Manage Players</h3>
    <p>
        The Players page allows users to create, view, edit, and delete player profiles.
        Player records include names, email addresses, phone numbers, skill levels,
        villages, wins, and losses.
    </p>

    <h3>Manage Tournaments</h3>
    <p>
        The Tournaments page allows users to create, view, edit, and delete tournament
        events. Each tournament includes a date, location, description, and maximum
        number of players.
    </p>

    <h3>Track Match Results</h3>
    <p>
        The Matches page allows users to record match results, including the players,
        winner, score, and match date.
    </p>

    <h3>View Leaderboard</h3>
    <p>
        The Leaderboard page ranks players based on wins and win rate.
    </p>

    <h3>Announcements</h3>
    <p>
        The Announcements page allows community updates to be created and managed.
    </p>

    <h3>Technology Stack</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>ASP.NET Core Blazor</li>
        <li>Entity Framework Core</li>
        <li>SQLite Database</li>
        <li>ASP.NET Core Identity Authentication</li>
        <li>Responsive CSS Design</li>
    </ul>
</div>